enigma2-plugin-extensions-sherlock (7.60) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix OE2.5 (DreamOS) compatibility for eTimer and callbacks.
  * Implement live network bitrate measurement for IPTV/TVHeadend streams.
  * Suppress temporary audio/video bitrate artifacts for IPTV streams.
  * Add HDD temperature display (requires hddtemp).
  * Switch bitrate widgets to Label for better UI stability.
  * Add hddtemp as recommended dependency.

